{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">No rigid classes</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/62s.gif?t=1726564264\" /><br>You can create <strong>your own class</strong>, nothing is locked, feel free to play as a fire mage wielding a two handed sword or a necro archer.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Tons of masteries and skills</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/7s.gif?t=1726564264\" /><br>There is a vast number of options to choose from when it comes to spells, weapons, abilities and masteries. You can create a ton of builds and constantly find new ways of crushing your enemies!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Old school action RPG hack and slash with skill based combat.</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/wyvern600x338.gif?t=1726564264\" /><br>Stats are important, but so is evading enemy attacks and aiming yours!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Open world full of quests</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/openWorld.png?t=1726564264\" /><br>Explore the world of Powerlust, travel between cities, find amazing treasures, help npcs find their lost teeth and more!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Made by one guy</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/5s.gif?t=1726564264\" /><br>Hobby project made by one guy (me). I spent quite a few years on it already. No huge corporations involved :)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Fun camera mods</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/4s.gif?t=1726564264\" /><br>Choose the way you play between Isometric, Top Down, TPP and FPP camera modes! Use fun camera filters to make the game look unique.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">I'd love to hear your feedback</h2>I'm still working on this game. I'd appreciate any feedback, it will be a really huge help in further development. Check out my twitter for constant updates and share your thoughts via email or <strong>discord</strong>!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Procedurally generated dungeons.       <br></li><li>Skill-based combat.       <br></li><li>No rigid classes.       <br></li><li>Tons of masteries, items, skills and builds.       <br></li><li>Open world to explore.       <br></li><li>Optional permadeath.       <br></li><li>Controller support.     <br></li><li>Awesome discord community.</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1726564264","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/page.bg.jpg?t=1726564264","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1726564264","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1726564264","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Cross-Platform Multiplayer","id":27},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"The game is about killing monsters, so naturally there is a lot of violence and gore involved."},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">No rigid classes</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/62s.gif?t=1726564264\" /><br>You can create <strong>your own class</strong>, nothing is locked, feel free to play as a fire mage wielding a two handed sword or a necro archer.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Tons of masteries a